text:
Ekaterina Romanenko Raevskaia (born 23 December 1993) is a Russian volleyball player.
Career.
She played at the 2015 Summer Universiade, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship. She played for WVC Dynamo Kazan.
